OL,3,CMP says source of water contamination
OL,4,Cfound - but 'boil warning' to last days
OL,6,FA warning for 16,000 properties in
OL,7,Fsouth Devon to boil tap water before
OL,8,Fusing it is likely to remain in place
OL,9,Ffor a further six or seven days,
OL,10,Faccording to the area MP.
OL,12,Fafter cryptosporidium - a parasite
OL,13,Fwhich causes a diarrhoea-like illness
OL,14,F- was found in its supply network in
OL,15,Fthe Brixham area.
OL,17,FPeople in Alston and Hillhead are
OL,18,Fbeing told to boil water before
OL,19,Fdrinking it, brushing their teeth, or
OL,20,Fusing it to prepare food.
