OL,6,FSo far 22 infections have been
OL,7,Fconfirmed - with many more people
OL,8,Freporting .
OL,10,FIn a statement, MP for the area
OL,11,FAnthony Mangnall said: "South West
OL,12,FWater believes it has located the
OL,13,Fsource of the issue and initiated a
OL,14,Ffix, but is continuing its
OL,15,Finvestigations and will be testing
OL,16,Ftheir network to ensure water is safe.
