OL,3,CMP says source of water contamination
OL,4,Cfound - but 'boil warning' to last days
OL,6,FIn the company's most recent update,
OL,7,Fits chief customer and digital officer
OL,8,FLaura Flowerdew said: "We sincerely
OL,9,Fapologise for the impact this is
OL,10,Fhaving on our customers in the Brixham
OL,11,Fand Alston areas.
OL,13,F"Protecting the health of our
OL,14,Fcustomers and providing them with a
OL,15,Fclean, fresh drinking water supply is
OL,16,Four number one priority and we will
OL,17,Fcontinue to work around the clock to
OL,18,Fmake sure that happens as soon as
OL,19,Fpossible."
